---SERVER
usage: python server.py [option=value] [option]...
	sh=serverHostname	Server hostname.
	sp=serverPort		Server port.
	nh=nsHostname		NameServer hostname.
	np=nsPort			NameServer port.
	ph=publishHost		The serverHostname to publish at the NameServer.
	g=group				The group to connect the server API at the NameServer.
	n=name				The name to connect the server API at the NameServer.
	f=file				File to initialize the server.
	h					Display this help menu.

---CLIENT
usage: python client.py [option=value] [option]...
	nh=hostname		NameServer hostname.
	np=port			NameServer port.
	g=group			The group to look up at the NameServer.
	f=file			File to initialize the client scheduler.
	b				Activates benchmarking.
	v				Activates debug.
	h				Display this help menu.
